      <section id="section_wpj_ntv_pzb" class="- topic/section ">
         <title class="- topic/title ">Purpose</title>
         <p class="- topic/p ">The purpose of this work instruction is to define the procedure for periodic sampling of
            stormwater after a storm event.</p>
      </section>
      <section id="section_a32_ptv_pzb" class="- topic/section ">
         <title class="- topic/title ">Application</title>
         <p class="- topic/p ">This work instruction applies to all Space employees and all operations, including
            manufacturing facilities, technical centers, offices, and administrative buildings where
            stormwater runoff may come in contact with industrial pollution.</p>
      </section>
